        {
            "title": "高盛料中國今年減息兩次 共0.2厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛對中國今年全年經濟增長預測為4.8%，較市場預期的4.5%略為樂觀。高盛首席中國經濟學家閃輝指出，對今年中國經濟看法較為正面，主因是對出口前景樂觀，且財政與貨幣政策仍寬鬆。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>預期2026經濟增長4.8%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閃輝預測，未來幾年中國出口每年仍有5%至6%增長，不僅因為中國商品的價格及成本低於其他國家，亦由於中國於稀土及不同產業鏈上具有自身優勢；她相信人行今年會減息兩次，每次0.1厘，另廣義赤字率今年按年料擴張1.2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c9dfa325-1ef4-346d-be1a-e772bcb94ac0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">關稅風險方面，閃輝指出對中國出口影響最大的關稅，可能是多國共同實施的協作關稅（coordinated tariff），現時國際地緣政治發展較複雜，令協作關稅難在中國身上發生。她又提到，中國本身很多出口並非消費品，而是屬於在海外設廠生產時會用到的中間物品（intermediate Goods）或資本物品（capital foods）。鑑於透過海外設廠的方式出海，對其他國家經濟會有帶動作用，她指中國出口未來具有一定可持續性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閃輝認同中國現時消費增速較弱，但隨着中國股市向上，最近也觀察到一些消費產業上的「綠芽」（green shoots），包括居民消費信心改善與工資小幅上升，其持續性還有待觀察。她補充，中國的服務業消費如旅遊及演唱會等，其增速優於商品消費。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF%E5%85%A9%E6%AC%A1-%E5%85%B10-2%E5%8E%98-182300487.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 02:37:31",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金融時報：SpaceX上市時間可能定在6月以契合天象及馬斯克生日",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據英國《金融時報》報導，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:馬斯克;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬斯克\">馬斯克</a>暗示，SpaceX可能把首次公開募股(<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:IPO;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/IPO\">IPO</a>)時間選在6月，以契合某個行星現象和他55歲生日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導引述五位知情人士的消息稱，這位火箭製造公司的掌門人考慮將上市時間定在金星與木星極度接近（金木合相）的時刻，這意味著IPO日期可能定於6月中旬，而馬斯克也恰好在該月迎來55歲生日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於大多數公司而言，這種決策邏輯簡直不可思議，但馬斯克長期以來就有在重大商業決策中融入象征意義和「玩梗」的習慣。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c631f729-caa0-33d3-9d8d-cc9e2b777586-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前，這位特斯拉老板曾發文稱要以每股420美元的價格將公司私有化，這被廣泛認為是在致敬大麻愛好者的「4·20」節日。而他將Twitter更名為X也被視為對早年創業的公司X.com的致敬（該公司在與PayPal 合併後失去了這個名字）。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《金融時報》指出，SpaceX計畫通過此次IPO籌集高達500億美元資金，公司估值約為1.5萬億美元。該IPO規模將為史上最大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SpaceX尚未對《金融時報》及彭博新聞的置評請求作出回應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Musk Eyes Timing SpaceX IPO With Planetary Alignment, FT Reports</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Kate Duffy.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-spacex%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%A86%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%A5%E5%A5%91%E5%90%88%E5%A4%A9%E8%B1%A1%E5%8F%8A%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5-161126993.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 01:27:39",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "穩定幣陣營再添重量級玩家 富達投資即將入場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 富達投資將推出自己的穩定幣，加入一系列有著類似意向的初創公司和金融機構行列。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該穩定幣名為「富達數字美元」（FIDD），將由富達數字資產國家協會發行。這家全國性信託銀行在12月獲得美國貨幣監理署的有條件運營許可。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們認為穩定幣有潛力成為基礎的支付和結算工具，」富達數字資產總裁Mike O’Reilly在接受彭博採訪時表示。「實時結算、全天候、低成本的資金管理，都是穩定幣能夠為我們的零售和機構客戶帶來的重要優勢。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9fd066d4-f7e3-3707-8e87-df91f4c2082c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fidelity Investments to Launch Stablecoin In Coming Weeks</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E5%B9%A3%E9%99%A3%E7%87%9F%E5%86%8D%E6%B7%BB%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F%E7%B4%9A%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6-%E5%AF%8C%E9%81%94%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4-145825359.html",
